title: Transformers Cybertronian Recognition Guide Volume 2 - Season 3
description:
This is the second volume of Cybertronian The Unofficial Transformers Recognition Guide which covers season three of the toys.

 The Cybertronian Recognition Guide has pictures of all the Transformers that were released that year, and all of their different transformations.  It also includes their tech specs and other miscellaneous information.

 I also have volumes 3, 4 and 5 scanned so far, if anyone is interested.
